text:
Worth it. Tutors teach very well. Attended their Sec Mathematics tuition for 4 years.

Also did their Add Maths tuition. It is very well taught.

I attained an A1 for Add Maths, and A2 for E Maths in O levels.

The only problem is to get more lessons when it is near exam times. There is not much slots available.
Highly recommend their Math tuition. Famous for teaching from a fail to a B grade in six months. Talented teachers.
